    <title>手机摄影学习笔记</title>
    <url>/2018/06/20/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%91%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="取景"><a href="#取景" class="headerlink" title="取景"></a>取景</h2><p>在混乱中建立一种美得秩序<br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-55cc533c38f93f36.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="一-取景方法"><a href="#一-取景方法" class="headerlink" title="一. 取景方法"></a>一. 取景方法</h3><h4 id="数字取景法"><a href="#数字取景法" class="headerlink" title="数字取景法"></a>数字取景法</h4><h5 id="1-三分法"><a href="#1-三分法" class="headerlink" title="1.三分法"></a>1.<strong>三分法</strong></h5><pre><code>横三分;  </code></pre><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-29da4b15fab9f5a7.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""><br>     竖三分;<br>     <img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-a1bef1303c504a33.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""><br>     九宫格;<br>     <img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-e64423eef93fb206.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""></p>
<h5 id="2-对称法"><a href="#2-对称法" class="headerlink" title="2. 对称法"></a>2. <strong>对称法</strong></h5><pre><code>横对称; 
![](https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-0c995caf66e8b7bf.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/620/format/webp)
竖对称; 
![](https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-e42940f753c4c20d.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/620/format/webp)
多发现;
![](https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-4d68e8663c49dd6e.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/620/format/webp)

*注意事项*:使用三分法和对称取景的时候,要让画面的线条保持水平或垂直,不要歪歪扭扭;可以多走动,往前往后,往上往下,寻找合适的取景.</code></pre><h4 id="引导取景法"><a href="#引导取景法" class="headerlink" title="引导取景法"></a>引导取景法</h4><h5 id="1-搭画框"><a href="#1-搭画框" class="headerlink" title="1. 搭画框"></a>1. <strong>搭画框</strong></h5><pre><code>引导观赏者看向画框里的人或景物.</code></pre><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-11db6ff20d56d7b7.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""><br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-e87d87c9a80e36c5.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""></p>
<h5 id="2-找纵深"><a href="#2-找纵深" class="headerlink" title="2. 找纵深"></a>2. <strong>找纵深</strong></h5><pre><code>用画面中延伸和汇聚的线条引导观赏者的视线. 
![](https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-9834fa25fe0df70a.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/620/format/webp)</code></pre><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-b8a805d4af703596.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""></p>
<h4 id="意蕴取景法"><a href="#意蕴取景法" class="headerlink" title="意蕴取景法"></a>意蕴取景法</h4><h5 id="1-留白"><a href="#1-留白" class="headerlink" title="1. 留白"></a>1. 留白</h5><pre><code>天空,墙面,湖面</code></pre><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-3c925c10389f66ba.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""><br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-0ebf0294612e3187.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""><br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-7f672c71b85fc9b9.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""></p>
<h5 id="2-动静对比"><a href="#2-动静对比" class="headerlink" title="2. 动静对比"></a>2. 动静对比</h5><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-c0fb2c133aacfbe8.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""><br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5738036-a2b259da6a9da987.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/620/format/webp" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p><img src="%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%91%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0_md_files/20200408134744.png?v=1&type=image" alt="取景方法总结"><br><img src="%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%91%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0_md_files/20200408134817.png?v=1&type=image" alt="常用"><br><img src="%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%91%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0_md_files/20200408134844.png?v=1&type=image" alt="摄影时注意事项"></p>
]]></content>
